{"tid":597004,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"想借恆生個免息現金plan","createTime":"2018-03-18T08:13:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T01:44:40.000Z","uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4e12124c4746575da893e3563148e66ae225821e","tid":597004,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T08:13:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hongkongloan.com/plan/hang-seng-bank/card-loan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongloan.com%2Fplan%2Fhang-seng-bank%2Fcard-loan&d=XdPyjybqQaprp66llt%2BsRV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=faebfc87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongloan.com/plan/hang-seng-bank/card-loan</a><br />\n<br />\n想問下有無巴打借左 <br />\n還錢係咪恆生講咁<br />\n假如我借左60000 分24個月還<br />\n咁每個月就還 2500 + 60000*0.18% ？？<br />\n仲有無其他費用？ 用信用卡還？"},{"pid":"d9921bb2d8cfef2e313e12b3ca8e15109b4787ce","tid":597004,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T08:19:13.000Z","msg":"有個表比你睇還幾多就幾多"},{"pid":"2c28edf9e0cce335029e14ff01ed5dbb96d86b44","tid":597004,"uid":28074,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T08:38:54.000Z","msg":"每個月還本金加利息，借兩年<br />\n本金：60000/24月=2500<br />\n利息：60000*1.8%（1年）=1080<br />\n           1080*2年=2160<br />\n            2160/24=90（每月）<br />\n<br />\n每月還款2500+90=2590<br />\n<br />\n借唔借？還得到先好借！"},{"pid":"54e1e93833b67f7d5cc325acd123c8c0f513e355","tid":597004,"uid":28074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c28edf9e0cce335029e14ff01ed5dbb96d86b44","tid":597004,"uid":28074,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T08:38:54.000Z","msg":"每個月還本金加利息，借兩年<br />\n本金：60000/24月=2500<br />\n利息：60000*1.8%（1年）=1080<br />\n           1080*2年=2160<br />\n            2160/24=90（每月）<br />\n<br />\n每月還款2500+90=2590<br />\n<br />\n借唔借？還得到先好借！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T08:44:46.000Z","msg":"睇錯左你個利息<br />\n0.18%(每月）*12=2.16%（年息）<br />\n將1.8%改做2.16%計先正確"},{"pid":"e43382d0705d4c5ede81e